    "description": "Lighten up brunch or dinner with this small but mighty Indian-style feast. You'll pan-fry golden pea and corn fritters, then top with a crispy sesame-fried egg, smashed cucumber and sweet chilli. Smaller portion providing 2 of your 5-a-day, a source of fibre and a source of protein.",
